high_descs: walk forwards to the end of the room, then turn right to face the bathroom sink
grab a spray bottle off of the bathroom sink counter
move to the right side of the bathroom sink counters enough so you can reach the top of the toilet
place the spray bottle down on top of the toilet
move to the left where you were before, and face the left side of the sink counter
grab another spray bottle off of the bathroom sink counter
move over to the right again where the toilet is and face the toilet
place the spray bottle down on top of the toilet on the right side next to the other spray bottle
anns.task_desc: place two spray bottles down on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn to your right walk towards the wall the face  the mirror on your right
Grab the pink spray bottle on the left
Walk across the room and turn to the toilet
Place the spray bottle on the top left side toilet tank
Turn around and head back to the sink counter
Grab the pink spray bottle on the sink counter
Turn around and walk to the toilet
Place the second pink spray bottle on the top right side of the toilet tank
anns.task_desc: Put the two pink spray bottle on the top of the toilet tank

high_descs: Walk straight, then turn to the right
Walk over to the bathroom counter
Pick up the spray bottle and turn around
Carry it over to the toilet
Set it down on the toilet
Walk back over to the counter
Pick up the other spray bottle that is on the counter
Walk it over to the toilet and sit it down by the other one
Head to the door and turn right.
Pick up the spray bottle on the left.
Turn right and cross the room to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
Turn left and cross the room to the door and turn right.
Pick up the spray bottle on the sink.
Turn right and cross the room to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on the toilet.
